      "title": "Tomorrow's power outage details have been released",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Public Utilities Commission has approved a three-hour power cut tomorrow (21) following a request from the Sri Lanka Electricity Board.",
        "Permission has been given to implement power cut for 1 hour 40 minutes during day and 1 hour 20 minutes at night in 20 zones from A to W.",
        "2 hours and 30 minutes from 6 am to 8.30 am in CC section and 3 hours blackout from 5.30 am to 8.30 am in M, N, O, X, Y and Z sections."
      ],
